## Visual Regression Testing

### When to Use

- Component library changes
- Theme or design token updates
- Layout modifications
- Responsive design changes

### Snapshot Management

- Review all visual diffs before approving
- Update baselines intentionally, never blindly
- Test across breakpoints: mobile (375px), tablet (768px), desktop (1280px)

---

## Accessibility Testing

### Automated (In CI)

```typescript
import { axe, toHaveNoViolations } from 'jest-axe';

expect.extend(toHaveNoViolations);

it('has no accessibility violations', async () => {
  const { container } = render(<MyComponent />);
  const results = await axe(container);
  expect(results).toHaveNoViolations();
});
```

### Coverage Requirements

| Component Type | Unit | Component | Integration | E2E | a11y |
|----------------|------|-----------|-------------|-----|------|
| Form | Yes | Yes | Yes | If critical | Yes |
| Data display | No | Yes | No | No | Yes |
| Navigation | No | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Interactive widget | Yes | Yes | Yes | If critical | Yes |
